desc_long							评测						"It’s made by someone who has spent a long, long time thinking about how to tell linear first-person stories, and who has found a new way to do it better than anyone else."– PC Gamer"Chung spins a memorable yarn, delivers it with confidence and panache, and trusts you to put all the loose ends back together."- Wired"What's truly impressive is the narrative weight and emotional impact it delivers in such a short span of time."- 8/10 ign.com												关于这款游戏							Explore the world of Thirty Flights of Loving through a first-person short story. In this sequel to Gravity Bone, take a deep dive with high-flying schemers, lovelorn criminals, and more stray kittens than you can shake a stick at. Saddle up, gunslinger.Featuring an original soundtrack by Chris Remo.						
